      "justification": "While this is a common issue in exploratory theoretical work and wouldn't alone invalidate the core idea, it highlights the fragility of the quantitative context provided. It means the specific 0.47% number is not robust, which is acceptable only if the authors strictly treat it as a toy demonstration, not as supportive evidence."
