      "severity": "MAJOR-REVISION",
      "justification": "If confirmed, the reported ~0.47% hit rate is likely anticonservative because the null does not include the actual search path that generated the hypothesis. This would not necessarily invalidate the descriptive coincidence, but it could substantially weaken or erase the claim that the match is unusually rare under a fair reference class."
